**Witherby Connect Virtual Library**
=====================================

**Reference Number:** cb-102-10688968

**Publication Date:** November 6, 2023

**Tender Closing Date:** December 5, 2023, 2:00 p.m. (Local Time)

**Brief Description**
-------------------

Transport Canada invites proposals to procure 50 concurrent Witherby Connect licenses to access International Maritime Organization (IMO) Conventions and Codes publications. The successful contractor will be required to maintain the library, ensuring new additions are available upon entering into force. The contract will be for a period of 5 years.

**Procurement Details**
------------------------

*   **Procurement Category:** Service (SRV)
*   **Procurement Method:** Competitive - Open Bidding
*   **Notice Type:** Request for Proposal
*   **Selection Criteria:** Lowest Price
*   **Trade Agreements:**

    *   Canada-Korea Free Trade Agreement (CKFTA)
    *   Canada-Honduras Free Trade Agreement
    *   Canada-Peru Free Trade Agreement (CPFTA)
    *   Canadian Free Trade Agreement (CFTA)
    *   Canada-Colombia Free Trade Agreement
    *   Canada-Panama Free Trade Agreement
*   **Regions of Opportunity:** Canada
*   **Regions of Delivery:** National Capital Region (NCR)
*   **Contracting Entity:** Transport Canada
*   **Contractor Point of Contact:**

    **Fanie Charron**
    **fanie.charron@tc.gc.ca**
    **(343) 574-8173** (Phone)

**Tender Documents**
--------------------

Tender documents, including response to clarification questions, are available on the Canada Buys website: [https://canadabuys.canada.ca](https://canadabuys.canada.ca)

**Attachments**
--------------
